    "data": [
        {
            "title": "OpenAI估值8520億美元面臨質疑,策略轉向引發關注",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 據英國《金融時報》週二援引投資者消息報導,隨著OpenAI調整策略以及人工智能板塊競爭加劇,該公司高達8520億美元的估值正面臨部分投資者的日益質疑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據《金融時報》報導,這家估值約8520億美元的公司正日益將重心轉向企業客戶,同時致力於捍衛其ChatGPT平台在消費者市場的主導地位,儘管該公司面臨來自競爭對手Anthropic的壓力不斷上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">一些投資者向《金融時報》表示,這一策略重新定位可能使OpenAI面臨風險,特別是在該公司準備最早於今年進行首次公開募股之際。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c262fa10-eb45-3cfa-8377-3235b5c4745c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導稱,鑑於該公司強勁的消費者增長勢頭,一位早期支持者對公司缺乏重點的問題表示擔憂。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《金融時報》報導,隨著Anthropic編碼工具需求激增,其年化收入在3月份飆升至約300億美元,而2025年底時為90億美元。相比之下,OpenAI在2月份的年化收入約為250億美元,儘管會計差異使得直接比較存在困難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">OpenAI高管為該策略進行了辯護,財務長Sarah Friar表示,該公司最近獲得的1220億美元融資反映了投資者的強力支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報導補充稱,儘管如此,一些投資者警告稱,競爭加劇和優先事項的演變可能會使OpenAI的增長軌跡變得複雜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/openai%E4%BC%B0%E5%80%BC8520%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91%E5%BC%95%E7%99%BC%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-053247147.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 13:43:36",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
