            "title": "大埔豪華海景洋房2,940萬沽 長揸15年仍輸953萬 呎價9千平過同區居屋！",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓市回溫，惟著名「蝕讓之城」大埔<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"比華利山別墅\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:比華利山別墅;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4coPyML\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">比華利山別墅</a>仍連錄大幅損手個案。屋苑3期一個雙號屋新近以約2,940萬元易手，呎價9,393元，平過同區居屋。原業主持貨約15年，仍蝕約953萬元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"單位放盤相\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wkT8cn3WQSPLFFZ.zNKYjQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/6c2d8f8196a532e60c660a2e55fee292\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">單位放盤相</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位放盤相</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"錦繡花園單號屋1,060萬沽 長情業主68萬買入 勁賺992萬升值14.6倍\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:錦繡花園單號屋1,060萬沽 長情業主68萬買入 勁賺992萬升值14.6倍;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4cHLAjx\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">錦繡花園單號屋1,060萬沽 長情業主68萬買入 勁賺992萬升值14.6倍</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"內地客6,365萬沽九肚尚珩洋房｜較9年前買入價大劈57% 連辣稅實蝕1.28億｜澳洲發展商接貨？\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:內地客6,365萬沽九肚尚珩洋房｜較9年前買入價大劈57% 連辣稅實蝕1.28億｜澳洲發展商接貨？;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4mv7tpG\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">內地客6,365萬沽九肚尚珩洋房｜較9年前買入價大劈57% 連辣稅實蝕1.28億｜澳洲發展商接貨？</a></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"單位放盤相\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EZjwhRkPCeoQYNQzYlL3Aw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/89d16c45da9e9050a86b0c25565557ba\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">單位放盤相</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位放盤相</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述成交單位為比華利山別墅3期湖景道雙號屋，實用面積3,130平方呎，屬5房3套間隔，連雙車位、前後花園及約765平方呎天台，原於28Hse網站叫價3,300萬元放盤，最新劈價至約2,940萬元沽出，呎價9,393元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d53e203b-09f9-3981-832e-21544d85b1c5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"單位放盤相\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MicEvB4QfFaKDPU7ZXrRGA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/7afbca7e6838513015cb0e95ee433174\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">單位放盤相</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位放盤相</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站放盤相可見，單位附豪華裝修，廳房均享遼闊海景，3樓全層為主人房連書房、衣帽間及套廁，面積極為寬敞。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"單位放盤相\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K3TaE19iLwPtuhch1DBLfg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/b9f7cc13f7730196e3fe11d963d2199d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">單位放盤相</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">單位放盤相</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">資料顯示，原業主2011年以約3,893萬元購入上述洋房，持貨約15年，是次易手賬面蝕讓約953萬元離場，期內貶值24%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據28Hse網站資料，<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"大埔區居屋\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:大埔區居屋;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/47Y1l3c\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大埔區居屋</a>新興花園近期平均成交呎價約10,684元，富雅花園、怡雅苑及逸雅苑近期平均成交呎價分別為約9,970元、9,820元及9,963元，均高過上述成交單位呎價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"